15); added an `Err` node + failure edge to the Mermaid DFD; noted the fail-open case in the copy-paste prompt.\n- **Test strategy / Files affected / Logging:** named the forced-error integration test and its file, and noted the server-side-only failure log.\n- Appended a **## Revision notes** section recording exactly what changed and the flag it closes.\n\n**Scope discipline:** no settled decisions reopened, no new scope introduced — only the fail-closed criterion and its supporting plan coverage. Frontmatter counts match the bodies in both files (acceptance.md: 15 criteria, AC1–AC15 present).\n\nFiles updated:\n- `/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/.pipeline/plan.md`\n- `/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/.pipeline/acceptance.md`\n\nStopping here — this was the single allowed revision pass; the human reviews the corrected plan next."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":16004,"cache_read_input_tokens":70664,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":16004,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcvvKxs83jnrqNyNzGEty","attributionAgent":"planning","type":"assistant","uuid":"2cec38a7-9338-492b-9005-ba33d5445914","timestamp":"2026-07-11T20:43:07.461Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"8b12bd3f-3c00-43c5-ad29-92ed49e714d3","version":"2.1.207","gitBranch":"feature/usage-daily"}
